metadata.name: Kodachi Unmasked #1
metadata.description:
Kodachi unMasked is a collection features 369 anime-inspired designs for holders to stake and earn.
As the new passive income, digital assets are here to stay, so we're getting our holders in the game right away.
With this NFT, you can stake for 6 months and receive a total return on investment (cost of NFT + profit) from the Kodachi Tokens they receive!
Our unMasked collection was created to allow earners to earn in a safe, simple, and secure way.
